  "excerpt": "David Chipperfield Architects has just completed a three-building scheme for the larger La Confluence master plan in Lyon, France designed by Herzog \u0026 de Meuron. View of the office building from one of the garden courtyards. Image: © Simon Menges The program includes a small office...",
